<figureCitation id="4EEDD7D9C753FF99439ABF2F6473FCA1" box="[160,277,799,825]" captionStart="FIGURE 8" captionStartId="13.[151,250,1463,1487]" captionTargetBox="[171,1423,181,1429]" captionTargetId="figure-17@13.[163,1424,181,1439]" captionTargetPageId="13" captionText="FIGURE 8. Type specimens and label data. A: lectotype of Atheta (Dimetrota) altaica; B: syntype of A. (D.) sublaevana [= A. (D.) atramentaria]; C: holotype of A. (D.) sulputrida [= A. (D.) atramentaria]; D: lectotype of A. (D.) furtiva; E: holotype of A. (D.) machonryongica; F: holotype of A. (D.) photaechonica; G: lectotype of A. (D.) subsericans; H: syntype of A. (Dimetrota) weisei; I: holotype of A. (D.) chagangensis = A. (Badura) tokiokai." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6571568" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6571568/files/figure.png" pageId="2" pageNumber="403">Fig. 8B–C</figureCitation>
